# path audiouri de test

4. ncrcm procesorul i modelul

In[]:
processor = Wav2Vec2Processor.from_pretrained(MODEL_DIR)
model = Wav2Vec2ForSequenceClassification.from_pretrained(MODEL_DIR)
model.eval()

device = torch.device("cuda" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu")
model = model.to(device)

5. Definim funcia de predicie

In[]:
def predict_emotion(path, max_length=16000):
    # incarcam fisierul audio la 16kHz mono
    speech, sr = librosa.load(path, sr=16_000, mono=True)

    # aplicam preprocesarea la fel ca in timpul antrenarii
    if len(speech) > max_length:
        speech = speech[:max_length]
    else:
        speech = np.pad(speech, (0, max_length - len(speech)), mode='constant')

    # extragem caracteristicile cu Wav2Vec2 processor
    inputs = processor(speech, sampling_rate=16_000, return_tensors="pt", padding=True)
    inputs = {k: v.to(device) for k, v in inputs.items()}

    # obtinem predictia facuta de model
    with torch.no_grad():
        logits = model(**inputs).logits

    # folosim softmax pentru a obtine probabilitatile
    probs = torch.nn.functional.softmax(logits, dim=-1)

    # obtinem predictia si nivelul de incredere al modelului
    pred_id = torch.argmax(logits, dim=-1).item()
    confidence = probs[0][pred_id].item()

    # mapare id -> label
    label = model.config.id2label[pred_id]

    # punem toate probabilitatile in format dictionar
    all_probs = {model.config.id2label[i]: probs[0][i].item() for i in range(len(model.config.id2label))}
    return label, confidence, all_probs

6. Rulm toate fiierele din folder-ul test_audio i afim rezultatele obinute

In[]:
audio_files = sorted(glob.glob(os.path.join(TEST_DIR, "*.wav")))
results = []

# mapare manuala etichete emotii pt formatul 2 (Ex: 1091_WSI_SAD_XX.wav)
label_map = {
    "ANG": "angry",
    "DIS": "disgust",
    "FEA": "fear",
    "HAP": "happy",
    "NEU": "neutral",
    "SAD": "sad",
    "SUR": "surprise"
}

for p in audio_files:
    filename = os.path.basename(p)
    # extragem label-ul adevarat din numele fisierului
    parts = filename.replace('.wav', '').split('_')

    if len(parts) == 3:
      true_label = parts[-1] # formatul_1 (Ex: OAF_bite_sad.wav)
    elif len(parts) >= 4:
      true_label = parts[-2] # formatul 2 (Ex: 1091_WSI_SAD_XX.wav)
    else:
      true_label = "unknown"

    # normalizare pentru eticheta
    true_label = label_map.get(true_label.upper(), true_label.lower())

    # predictia si nivelul de incredere
    pred_label, confidence, all_probs = predict_emotion(p)

    results.append({
        "file": filename,
        "true_emotion": true_label,
        "predicted_emotion": pred_label,
        "confidence": confidence,
        "all_probabilities": all_probs
    })

# cream un DataFrame cu rezultatele obtinute
df_results = pd.DataFrame(results)

# salvare rezultate csv
# formatam coloana confidence ca sir cu virgula zecimala
df_results["confidence"] = df_results["confidence"].apply(lambda x: f"{x:.6f}".replace('.', ','))
# scriere CSV
df_results[["file", "true_emotion", "predicted_emotion", "confidence"]].to_csv(
    "rezultate_predictii.csv", index=False, sep=';')

# afisare detaliata rezultate
pd.set_option('display.max_rows', None)
pd.set_option('display.width', None)
print("Detailed Prediction Results:")
print(df_results[["file", "true_emotion", "predicted_emotion", "confidence"]].to_string(index=False))

In[]:
# matricea de confuzie
def plot_confusion_matrix():
    true_labels = df_results["true_emotion"]
    pred_labels = df_results["predicted_emotion"]

    # extragem etichetele unice
    labels = sorted(set(true_labels) | set(pred_labels))

    # cream matricea de confuzie
    cm = confusion_matrix(true_labels, pred_labels, labels=labels)

    # graifc
    plt.figure(figsize=(7, 5))
    sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt="d", cmap="Blues", xticklabels=labels, yticklabels=labels)
    plt.xlabel("Predicted Emotion")
    plt.ylabel("True Emotion")
    plt.title("Confusion Matrix")
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

plot_confusion_matrix()

# probabilitatile emotiilor pentru fiecare clasa
def plot_emotion_probabilities(results_df):
    # extragem emotiile din probabilitatile primului rezultat
    emotions = list(results_df.iloc[0]["all_probabilities"].keys())

    # cream un nou DataFrame cu probabilitatile emotiilor
    probs_df = pd.DataFrame()
    probs_df["file"] = results_df["file"]
    probs_df["true_emotion"] = results_df["true_emotion"]

    # adaugam coloane pentru probabilitati
    for emotion in emotions:
        probs_df[emotion] = results_df["all_probabilities"].apply(lambda x: x[emotion])

    # grafic
    plt.figure(figsize=(8, 30))

    # pregatim datele pentru afisare
    plot_data = []
    for _, row in probs_df.iterrows():
        for emotion in emotions:
            plot_data.append({
                "File": row["file"],
                "Emotion": emotion,
                "Probability": row[emotion],
                "True Emotion": row["true_emotion"]
            })

    plot_df = pd.DataFrame(plot_data)

    # cream heatmap
    pivot_df = plot_df.pivot(index="File", columns="Emotion", values="Probability")
    sns.heatmap(pivot_df, cmap="viridis", annot=True, fmt=".2f")
    plt.title("Emotion Probabilities for Each Test File")
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

plot_emotion_probabilities(df_results)

8. Interpretarea datelor n funcie de fiierul .csv obinut

Funcii Excel folosite

Pentru celula E2:
=IF(B2=C2;TRUE;FALSE)
Pentru celula F2:
=IF(D2>50%;TRUE;FALSE)

Pentru celula E122:
=COUNTIF(E2:E121;TRUE)
Pentru celula F122:
=COUNTIFS(F2:F121;TRUE;E2:E121;TRUE)

Din cele 120 de fiiere rulate, 74 au fost clasificate corect n funcie de emoie. Dintre acestea, 63 au avut un scor de ncredere mai mare de 50%.
